            "description": "Unique temporary identifier for this comment. Format: 'aw_' followed by 3 to 12 alphanumeric characters (e.g., 'aw_abc1', 'aw_Test123'). Auto-generated if not provided. The temporary ID is returned in the tool response so you can reference this comment later.\n\n{pattern: \"^aw_[A-Za-z0-9]{3,12}$\"}",
            "type": "string"
